Line1.EECAE: I feed on pain. The relics sustain me. They let me walk Sanctuary without needing to kill.
Line3.EECAE: I like it here. Humans enjoy many small pleasures. Fresh bread. Soft sheets. Mulled wine. Don't know how long. But for now, I stay.
Line5.EECAE: He helps me. I’m alive, and I’m free. Not many can say the same.
MenuLabel: “What do you both get out this...arrangement?”
